# Money Pages vs Conversion Landings (Ilyashan)

## Conversion landing pages — DO NOT convert to long-form articles

These pages are sales-focused landings. Keep short emotional copy + visual sections (hero, essence, emotions, journey, FAQ, CTA). Never inject 2.500+ word article overlays into these routes:

- `/fensterreinigung` and `ServiceHubLanding`
- `/gutschein` and `/gutschein/*` (`GiftLanding`)
- `/fensterreinigung/*` (`PackageLanding`)
- `/locations/*` (`LocationLanding`)

CTA on landings: **Preis jetzt berechnen** → `/de/angebot` (UTM) or **Gutschein bestellen** → TreuePay (UTM).

## Long-form SEO — allowed on intent & ratgeber only

- `/intent/*` (e.g. fensterputzer-aachen, glasreinigung-baesweiler)
- `/ratgeber/*`

Each SEO page must be unique, intent-specific, native German, with schema and internal links.

## Content language

All user-facing content in German at native quality. Fensterreinigung sector tone: Klarheit, Vertrauen, Streifenfrei, Zeit schenken.
